fields.name: Yoga Mat - Navy Blue
fields.description: The lightweight mat only weighs 2.3kg, so it’s easy to carry to class and the 4mm cushioned gives your hips and joints the support you need. The center line and iconic moon phases are engraved into the surface to help you stay connected and balanced through every transition. Natural rubber, free of PVC or other harmful substances. Rubber yoga mats are 99% latex free, and safe for most people with a latex hypersensitivity. In case of a very severe allergy, contact with the mat is not recommended.

The crisp yet energizing all-natural citrus scent elevates your awareness. NATURAL INGREDIENTS: The Asutra 100% natural and organic yoga mat spray has been handcrafted by yoga clean freaks. This proprietary formula keeps all mats clean while adding a boost for your mind, body, and soul. ECO-FRIENDLY: Asutra Yoga Mat Detox is an all-natural cleaner made with organic essential oils to keep your mats and props clean and smelling fresh. No harsh ingredients. NO PARABENS, PHOSPHATES, OR BLEACH: Asutra's 100% natural and organic Yoga Mat Cleaner is hand-made with love. It is free from parabens, phosphates, and bleach and contains zero harsh chemicals. fields.name: Reclaim Eco Yoga Brick - Black
fields.description: Bricks are ideal for adding lift or grounding in all manner of poses. They can help stabilise and add height in standing and balancing poses or can be placed between the knees to activate the inner leg muscles. The ultimate zero waste choice made from post production waste. Bevelled edges and corners for additional comfort and an easier hand grip. Extra durable and scratch resistant. Light enough to carry between classes, yet sturdy enough to bear your weight in postures. If you'd like to go for a larger size, please find it here. Made in Spain

fields.name: Cork Yoga Wheel
fields.description: Evolve and deepen your yoga practice with our Cork Yoga wheel. It’s a revolutionary prop that offers a wide variety of physical benefits and support with challenging postures. With our yoga wheel you can enhance flexibility, strengthen the full body and improve balance and stability. Yoga wheels are fun, dynamic and challenging! Our cork yoga wheel is made from the bark of the cork oak tree, which is a renewable and recyclable resource. Cork bark is naturally antibacterial, eradicating germs and bacteria that cause bad odors, so you can breathe easy knowing that your cork yoga wheel isn’t home to any nasties.

fields.name: Diamond Yogashorts
fields.description: Our Diamond Yogashorts feature takes the pressure off when you move and flow. Very comfortable. Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this gorgeous garment. Material: Recycled PET Fabric. Oeko-Tex Earth Passport Certified Inks in production.

fields.name: Balance Cinnamon - Gray
fields.description: Join us in celebrating our planet with these Recycled Plastic Bottle Leggings from our friends in the US Wolven Threads. We are using 27.6 Plastic Bottles for each and every pair of Leggings here. 1.9 Gallons of water are saved with each pair of Leggings also! This is amazing and something we are ready to celebrate. The Heliocentric design is superb. A high waist makes these leggings super supportive and flattering. We are loving the softness of this fabric, it is divine against the skin. They are Limited Edition and will last just a short time. Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this gorgeous garment

fields.name: Enchanted Recycled Leggings
fields.description: There is a pocket at the back of the waistband that easily fits your keys or phone so you can take The Enchanted Recycled Leggings running if you like that! We created the sweetest details for the Enchanted Leggings. The Waistband is a double layer so it is sculpting as well as supportive.  The High Waistband allows your tummy to move easily yet holds you in and we all love that! The seams are detailed so they fit like a glove and remain in place whilst you take them to whatever practice you feel to do! Material: Recycled Nylon woven into a High Performance fabric.

fields.name: Layla Flares - Aubergine
fields.description: The Waist Band details are divine and sculpt your torso whilst remaining super comfortable. The lines of The Layla Flares Recycled Leggings are totally superb! The seam details are amazing and serve to bring the Layla Flares Recycled Leggings close to the body and to support you. They are Full Length and ready for the strongest of practices or exercise routines ever!

fields.name: The Enchanted Recycled Leggings - Petrol
fields.description: There is a pocket at the back of the waistband that easily fits your keys or phone so you can take The Enchanted Recycled Leggings running if you like that! We created the sweetest details for the Enchanted Leggings. The Waistband is a double layer so it is sculpting as well as supportive.  The High Waistband allows your tummy to move easily yet holds you in and we all love that! The seams are detailed so they fit like a glove and remain in place whilst you take them to whatever practice you feel to do! Material: Recycled Nylon woven into a High Performance fabric.

fields.name: The Enchanted Recycled Leggings - Black
fields.description: There is a pocket at the back of the waistband that easily fits your keys or phone so you can take The Enchanted Recycled Leggings running if you like that! We created the sweetest details for the Enchanted Leggings. The Waistband is a double layer so it is sculpting as well as supportive. The High Waistband allows your tummy to move easily yet holds you in and we all love that! The seams are detailed so they fit like a glove and remain in place whilst you take them to whatever practice you feel to do! Material: Recycled Nylon woven into a High Performance fabric.

fields.name: Dakini Pine - Petrool
fields.description: We adore the Rayon Lycra fabric that we have chosen to work with. This is very strong yet light and easy to wear. This fabric holds it shape and does not create knees when you bend. The waist band is a delightful detail, supportive and secure. We have included a draw string for those of you that want extra care and security for your pants. Take the time to choose these beloved pants and the world will smile with you.

fields.name: Chill Pants - Beige
fields.description: The Chill Pants are some of the most comfortable and easy to wear Yoga Pants we have ever made. Created from our Natural Fibres they are a pleasure on the body! The waist band is ultra supportive and easy to wear. The legs are cut loose with a gather at the hem. This is a very flattering pair of Yoga Pants. Please wash these in cold water and line dry under the suns rays as we hope to help you keep these pants for time to come.

fields.name: Aladin Pants - Black
fields.description: These Aladin Pants are fitting closer on the bottom and moving down to a boot leg ankle. We cannot argue with that. We have included a string tie in these pants. This makes it your choice how tight or how loose you enjoy to wear these pants. The cotton lycra we use for these pants is wonderful. Full of stretch and movement whilst being supportive at the same time. Red completes the picture and there is enough choice to bring two pairs of these darlings home with you. We love to practice yoga and exercise and we also like to look good whilst doing it. At Just Yoga we make pants that you can be happy to wear on and off the mat. Please feel free to wash these beauties in the machine but take the time to line dry under the suns rays. We realise that machine clothes dryers shorten the life of most garments and we love these pants so much we are sure you will not want to do that.

fields.name: Emana High Waist Leggings - Orange
fields.description: We are delighted to share with you our 'Smart Fibre' Emana Leggings in High Waist in Full Length. We created these for you with a bioactive fibre that works with your body.  This fabric massages the upper layers of your skin and increases blood flow which then works to heat your body. This then helps you release toxins and to reduce cellulite. An amazing fabric that we are just loving to wear and use. We made these High Waist with our Lotus Flower sitting on the back of the waistband. They are supportive and feel really so good on the body.  Currently the Emana Leggings are our go to for all styles of exercise and yoga practice. Full length and full of love. You will love these as much as we do we are certain of it. Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful garment. We recommend never using a machine dryer for our clothing.

fields.name: Dharma Harem - Black
fields.description: Fantastic Dharma Harem made from divine rayon lycra. This fabric is so sweet against the skin. We love these pants and these are the ones we wear on the plane. Staying warm whilst looking good as we wing our way across the ocean. Never has flying, yoga and style been combined so well. This fabric is extremely strong and has great stretch capabilities. Perfect for any yoga practice and looks totally divine on the body. Easy to wash and just as easy to dry under the suns rays, we are sure you will love these pants as much as we do. Why not wear this reminder on your hip and feel the love! Details are up to the minute for fashion and functional for a yoga practice. Gathered at the ankle in style, these pants look and feel great. Flattering to all shapes and sizes, we love these pants!!! Fully machine washable and durable, we stand behind these yoga pants.

fields.name: Noor Leggings
fields.description: We are thrilled to share with you these beautiful Noor Recycled Plastic Bottle Leggings from our friends at Wolven Threads in the US. These beauties use 27.6 Recycled Plastic Bottles for each and every pair of Leggings. They also save 1.6 Gallons of water for each pair. This is amazing and the way forward for you and the Planet. We made a high waist for you to support and protect. This is incredibly comfortable and you will be surprised how utterly soft this fabric feels against the skin. We are loving wearing these all day and we dont take them off after practice. Take these home and give the planet a rest. You will be happy you did so. These Noor Leggings are the way forward for all of us. Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful pair of leggings

fields.name: Urban Tank - Black
fields.description: Created out of the softest Cotton Lycra which is super strong.  You can practice a very dynamic form of yoga or any other exercise pursuit in this one! A Racerback detail accentuates your shoulder blades.

fields.name: Scrumptious Top
fields.description: This garment is extremely supportive and a delight to wear. We wear the Top Scrumptious when we are practicing a strong practice and for just cruising through life. It is elegant and the back detail is very beautiful. Very supportive for women's breasts with the in built shelf bra. We love to practice yoga but we enjoy to be supported and in the Top Scrumptious you will be just that! We think the Top Scrumptious is a wonderful addition to your yoga wardrobe. Wear it well and practice yoga. Wash in the machine but please dry on the line. Clothing dryers shorten the lifespan of your garments.

fields.name: Karna Cami Tank - Blue
fields.description: The new High Performance Collection is amazing! 4 way stretch fabric that provides you with an ease of movement and strength is utterly divine!  We love to wear this garment everywhere! Quick Dry in nature, this is perfect for swimming if you want to! We adore the Karna Cami Tank and cannot wait to share it with you in this freshly landed High Performance Collection. The fabric is super strong and lasts so well!

fields.name: Dharma Top - Black
fields.description: The Dharma Top is our newest Yoga Tank. We have created a stunning back detail on this wonderful garment. The straps are very supportive and we have included rubber to keep them in place. The inbuilt shelf bra provides support and our Natural Fibre Rayon Lycra is a dream to practice in. Perfect for nearly all styles of yoga practice and everyday living.

fields.name: Cable Top - Black
fields.description: The Cable Top really does live up to its name. We created for you a sublime detail on the back of this garment. Texture and support come together to create one of our most lovely Yoga Tanks. This garment is perfect for a strong practice and just as divine out on the street all day long. Natural fibre Rayon Lycra is soft but so incredibly strong. We keep ours on all day long and know you will too. The front is gorgeous and offers coverage and support to nearly all shapes and sizes of breasts. We recommend washing in cold water and line drying under the suns rays.

fields.name: SuperLove Sweatshirt - Gray
fields.description: Midweight, 50% Cotton/50% Polyester fleece, with up to 5% made from recycled plastic bottles. Soft, 7.5-Oz cotton blend provides comfort in any climate. Sweatshirt sits just below your natural waistline. Ribbed hem and cuffs keep their shape. High-stitch density, so it lasts longer without pilling. Tag-free for added comfort.

fields.name: Sweetheart Long Sleeve - Petrol
fields.description: The Sweetheart Long Sleeve has a wider boat neckline than the others. This is a super easy style to wear. Accentuating your collar bones and the curve of your torso, this is a flattering style. 3/4 length sleeves make a perfect transitional piece for all temperatures. We love the curved hemline of the Sweetheart Long Sleeve. Please wash the Sweetheart Tie Dye in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful garment. Material: Light weight cotton. Hand dye for individual colour ways

fields.name: Sweetheart Long Sleeve - Purple
fields.description: The Sweetheart Long Sleeve has a wider boat neckline than the others. This is a super easy style to wear. We love the curved hemline of the Sweetheart Long Sleeve. Please wash the Sweetheart Tie Dye in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful garment. Material: Light weight cotton. Hand dye for individual colour ways

fields.name: Shirt Hoodie 'Breathe' - Black
fields.description: Hoodie Breathe is one of our favourites and this version keeps getting better! Natural cotton allows your body to breathe and move easily. Stretch keeps the movement flowing and we adore that. Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays so that this divine garment stays with you for time to come.

fields.name: Perfect T - White
fields.description: The Perfect T is our go to for a comfy natural fibre T Shirt. The Perfect T works when paired with all of our leggings and Hot Pants so please choose wisely as we have them in all the colours and know that you will want that also! Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful garment! Material: Superb light weight cotton fabric.

fields.name: Perfect T - Black
fields.description: The Perfect T is our go to for a comfy natural fibre T Shirt. The Perfect T works when paired with all of our leggings and Hot Pants so please choose wisely as we have them in all the colours and know that you will want that also! Please wash in cold water and line dry under the suns rays to extend the life of this beautiful garment! Material: Superb light weight cotton fabric.

fields.name: Warrior T-Shirt - Green
fields.description: Pima Cotton Fabric: 88% Pima Cotton, 12% Spandex. Pima cotton fabric: Ultra-Soft & Skin-Friendly fabric, which is highly stretchy and lightweight as feather. Athletic crew neck shirts for men. Various Solid Color T-shirts ensure to meet your needs for matching with casual pants or jeans, etc. Short sleeve tees for men: Made of 4-way stretch fabric that's breathable and stretchy, also with function of high resistance to abrasion.

fields.name: Easy Wrap Top - Black
fields.description: Plunging surplice V-neckline design for a fashion and easy to wear. Long sleeve crop top,comfortable soft and good stretchy material suitable for autumn,winter,fall. Sexy self-tie criss cross straps details in front. Great go with casual pants,skirts,shorts or jeans. Slim fit surplice crop top with beautifully drapery,detailed size info please check product description.

fields.name: Recharge Joggers
fields.description: Designed to keep you comfortable anywhere you go, these ultra-soft fleece joggers are the definition of comfort. Premium materials and fabrics allow your body to breathe and move. We choose premium fabrics that are long lasting and durable, soft on the skin and designed specifically for yoga lifestyle.

fields.name: Anywhere Shorts
fields.description: The Anywhere Short is made for hot yoga and more intense flows. The nylon blend fabric creates a super stretchy, soft and quick-drying short. The front right hand side has an invisible zip pocket for storing valuables. The back left hand side has a towel loop so you can be ready when the heat starts to build up.

fields.name: Tech Tee
fields.description: Crafted from our PRO tech fabric, this performance tee is the best match for any workout. It’s moisture-wicking properties and breathability will keep you cool no matter the challenge.

fields.name: Lunge Shorts Colorblock
fields.description: Designed for the minimalist guy who wants an easy two-in-one short, this pair boasts sweat wicking capabilities, pockets for the essentials and a comfortable built in brief. Wash & dry in low temperatures to prolong garment shelf life while also conserving energy. Always avoid using fabric softeners – they can inhibit wicking and breathability in performance fabrics. Do not dry clean.

fields.name: Yoga Hand Towel
fields.description: Absorbent and quick drying, the eQua® Hand Yoga Towel is the perfect accessory to any yoga mat. Lay the towel on your mat under your hands (or feet) for extra grip and less slip. This small towel is easy to place wherever extra grip is needed throughout your practice. Featuring sweat activated grip, so the more you sweat the better the grip. The eQua® Hand Yoga Towel supports not only your yoga practice, but can be used at the gym, camping, or whenever you're on the go. To prevent color bleeding, we recommend washing your eQua® towels twice with similar colors before use. Using a dark towel with a light mat may result in color transfer unless washed first.

fields.name: Yoga Mat Towel - Purple
fields.description: The most trusted performance yoga towel in the world, yogitoes® help prevent slipping as you start to flow and sweat. Lay this towel on top of your mat to enhance your yoga practice. Ultra absorbent, lightweight and quick drying, yogitoes® features our patented Skidless® Technology, which utilizes silicone nubs to grip your mat and keep you in place. Ideal for hot yoga or any sweaty practice and durable enough to take anywhere: the beach, the gym, Pilates or traveling. Eco-friendly, every towel is made with at least four recycled plastic bottles.

fields.description: Ideal carry all yoga mat bag in organic cotton. Zipper along the bag ensuring easy in and out with the mat. Zipped pocket for smaller necessities. Adjustable carry strap. Size: 73 cm x 17 cm diameter, Weight: 0,32 kg, Material: 100% organic cotton.

fields.description: Length: 42 cm, height from front: 14,5 cm, height from behind: 17,5 cm, with: 20 cm, weight: 1.7 kg, material: Birch wood
